# SBIePay Repo Governance

Applies the standard governance baseline to GitLab application repositories —
from a pipeline or from a laptop.

Platform: GitLab Ultimate 18.1.6-EE (`gitlab.sbi`), air-gapped
Scope: application repos under `itepaypg-sbiepay2/application/`

